---
---
<section class="min-h-screen p-4 md:p-8 relative z-10 my-32">
  <div class="b-grid h-full">
    
    <!-- Sticky Sidebar -->
    <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-3">
      <div class="sticky top-32">
        <h2 class="brutal-title text-5xl md:text-8xl mb-8">THE<br/>GUTS.</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 font-bold uppercase text-sm border-t-2 border-theme pt-4">
          <span class="flex justify-between"><span>Engine</span> <span>Go / SQLite</span></span>
          <span class="flex justify-between"><span>Auth</span> <span>SigV4 / Bearer</span></span>
          <span class="flex justify-between"><span>UI</span> <span>SvelteKit / OpenTUI</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content Area -->
    <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-8 md:col-start-5 mt-20 md:mt-0 flex flex-col gap-32">
      
      <!-- Block 1 -->
      <article class="shape-container p-8 md:p-16 hover:bg-(--accent-color)! hover:text-[#111]! transition-all duration-500 group relative overflow-hidden">
        <i class="ph-duotone ph-database text-[15rem] absolute -right-10 -bottom-10 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-30 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all"></i>
        <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl brutal-title mb-8 relative z-10">Data before<br/>Metadata</h3>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-2xl max-w-xl font-bold leading-relaxed relative z-10">
          Write to .tmp. Rename atomically. Insert to SQLite. 
          If the row isn't there, the data isn't there.
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- Block 2 -->
      <article class="border-4 border-theme p-8 md:p-16 relative bg-transparent overflow-hidden group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-(--text-color) translate-y-full group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-500 ease-in-out"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10 group-hover:text-(--bg-color) transition-colors duration-500">
          <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl brutal-title mb-8">Zero-Copy<br/>Egress</h3>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-2xl max-w-xl font-bold leading-relaxed">
            We bypass userspace completely. Linux sendfile() blasts bits straight from disk to network socket.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Block 3 -->
      <article class="shape-container p-8 md:p-16 bg-(--text-color)! text-(--bg-color)! flex flex-col items-start relative">
        <div class="bg-(--accent-color) text-black font-bold px-4 py-1 uppercase text-sm mb-8 inline-block -rotate-2">
          Checksum Pipeline
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl brutal-title mb-8">TeeReader<br/>Validation</h3>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-2xl max-w-xl font-bold leading-relaxed opacity-80">
          Hashing data as it streams to disk. MD5 & x-amz-checksums verified at wire speed. Corrupt data dies before it lives.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>